      "content": "okay i'll try scraping it back. but honestly the more i look at these cracks, the more it feels like they're appearing in weird patterns, like they're coming from inside the wall itself. do you think there's something wrong with the studs or the framing that would cause stuff to keep popping up in these specific spots?",
